       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. TESTHELLO.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-MESSAGE.
          05 WS-GREETING    PIC X(20) VALUE 'Hello from COBOL!'.
          05 WS-STATUS      PIC X(10) VALUE 'SUCCESS'.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PROCEDURE.
           DISPLAY WS-GREETING.
           DISPLAY 'Status: ' WS-STATUS.
           STOP RUN.
